<p>Hello <%= @resource.email %>!</p>

<p>Someone has made a request to change your password. Follow the link below to change password.</p>

<p><%= link_to 'Change my password', edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token) %></p>

<p>If this wasnt you, please ignore this email.</p>
<p>Your passwrord will not change until the link has been followed and new password set.</p>
